replies.body:
I like to play Lissandra in this mode. CC is the bane of all these hypercarries.

I don't even get damage on her. I just pick up RoA, Moonfire and then itemise against their team. Thornmail, Randuin's, Sunfire and Frozen Heart if they're mostly AD. Abyssal Scepter, Odyn's Veil, Merc Treads, Locket if they're mostly AP.

Long live the Lissandra tank! {{champion:127}}
